You can define the types for all these files with `*.comp` in a `declerations.d.ts` file (or whatever name you choose).

```typescript
declare module &quot;*.comp&quot; {
  const value: any; // Add better type definitions here if desired.
  export default value;
}
```

You may need to also add this to `typeRoots` in your `tsconfig.json`

```json
{
    &quot;compilerOptions&quot;: {
        // Other configuration...
        &quot;typeRoots&quot;: [
            &quot;./src/declerations.d.ts&quot;
        ]
    }
}
```

And now, `import value from &quot;./test.comp&quot;` should work as expected (at least the types).

